                "invention-title": [
                    "Integrated reaction device and method for co-producing green hydrogen through conversion of shrimp and crab shells under solar catalysis",
                    "太阳能催化虾蟹壳转化联产绿氢的一体化反应装置及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses an integrated reaction device and method for solar catalysis conversion of shrimp and crab shells and co-production of green hydrogen, and the method comprises the following steps: putting untreated shrimp and crab shells into a material barrel, simultaneously ensuring that the interior of a pretreatment reactor is an alkaline environment, descending the material barrel into the pretreatment reactor at a constant speed by using a driving device, and carrying out reaction; after the materials are fully dissolved, opening a valve to enable pretreatment reaction liquid to flow into and fill an anode chamber of the photoelectrocatalysis reactor, ensuring circular flow of the reaction liquid by utilizing a pump, introducing seawater into a cathode chamber by utilizing the pump, then driving the photoelectrocatalysis reaction by utilizing electric energy stored by a solar photovoltaic panel, and after the reaction is fully carried out, carrying out the photoelectrocatalysis reaction. Reaction liquid in the anode chamber is led out to a product collecting bottle, and hydrogen generated in the cathode chamber is stored through a gas collecting bag, so that an integrated process of converting shrimp and crab shells and seawater into high-value chemicals and fuels under the driving of solar energy is realized."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种太阳能催化虾蟹壳转化联产绿氢的一体化反应装置及方法，该方法包括将未经处理的虾蟹壳置于物料桶中，同时保证预处理反应器中为碱性环境，利用驱动装置将物料桶匀速下降至预处理反应器中后，使物料桶匀速转动，待物料充分溶解后，打开阀门使预处理反应液流入并充满光电催化反应器阳极室，利用泵保证反应液的循环流动，同时利用泵将海水引入阴极室，随后使用太阳能光伏板储存的电能驱动光电催化反应进行，待充分反应后，将阳极室反应液导出至产物收集瓶，阴极室产生的氢气则通过收集气袋进行储存，实现了太阳能驱动下的虾蟹壳及海水向高值化学品及燃料转化的一体化流程。"
                }
            ]
